{"tid":1545854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"CLS，BB奶粉尿片，每個brand 年年都畀成一億落TVB廣告","createTime":"2019-09-06T05:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T07:19:22.000Z","uid":267969,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"3f331263321b7aa2c2380ed6f0c076bbd0a5794f","tid":1545854,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又俾FB 壓低閱讀數字<br />\n抵制TVB團隊仝人，跪求大家share 出去</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/frBGY1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfrBGY1T.jpg&h=750518a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/446655749524613/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.417570699099785%2F446655749524613%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=fe7bb788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/446655749524613/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【罷買人血奶粉尿片】良心從小開始培養</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根據廣告界線報，以下每個嬰兒品牌每年至少<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用5000千萬，甚至1億落TVB廣告</span></span></strong>，間接供養無綫新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n奶粉可以畀到BB 好多營養、多方面發展，但如果無咗良心，BB第日幾叻都好，你作為父母仲會為佢驕傲？<br />\n喺依家嘅環境，我哋唔知未來會變成點，但父母最大嘅心願，一定係孩子可以做個正直、有良心嘅人。支持良心品牌！<br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【傳送門已開，立即行動，喚醒品牌良心！】</strong></span><br />\n1. 比嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 真實用家貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，產品圖寫口號 (用家適用)<br />\n3. 留言</span><br />\n***<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">【奶粉】</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美素佳兒：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frisohk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrisohk%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4f0bd1f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frisohk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美贊臣：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/meadjohnsonhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmeadjohnsonhk%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=b9d7d73e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/meadjohnsonhk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 牛欄牌：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CGHappyKids/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCGHappyKids%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=4a3403fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CGHappyKids/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雅培：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/abbotthk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fabbotthk%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=db3e0d2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/abbotthk/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Aptamil：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AptaHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAptaHK%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=95d91d5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AptaHK/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislik