a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Pampers ：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PampersBBClub/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPampersBBClub%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=6798c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PampersBBClub/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>※留言Template</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無綫新聞，誤導市民！寧願條片爆晒要換得密啲，都唔想BB用無良心品牌，罷買TVB廣告商，我會轉用moony!<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n【TVB廣告客戶名單，消費前請諗清楚】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=308d373e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a><br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－<br />\n請即follow:<br />\nFB: #sayno2tvb or 五毛電視cctvb - 廣告宣傳部<br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/shittytvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fshittytvb%2F&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=2ceaadc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/shittytvb/</a><br />\nTG 抵制廣告行動組: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H0ngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=072cb4b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a>"},{"pid":"b25ea4e52537f5082703abd074ebc0bf674d2c9c","tid":1545854,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:08:51.000Z","msg":"tui this"},{"pid":"44c0745dc555c3a4835c4698135cd24c93606339","tid":1545854,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 終極文宣 對準政權 全民抗共</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%